There are random words, could be any characters or special symbols in them.
We only care about the characters in the words
exp: we are so happey, the day comes.semoc yad eht ?yeppah os era ew,
we say this is palindrome.
Of course, "abcba" also is
stdin
return True if it is palindrome

test cases:
we are so happey, the day comes.semoc yad eht ?yeppah os era ew,
abcdcba
abvvvcsd
